graph TD
    %% OJS Complete Workflow with Autonomous Agents
    
    %% Author Journey
    A1[Logistics_Warehouse] --> A2[Logistics_FleetManagement]
    A2 --> A3[Logistics_FleetManagement]
    A3 --> A4[Logistics_DeliveryRoute]
    A4 --> A5[Logistics_Warehouse]
    
    %% Autonomous Agents for Authors
    RA[Logistics_TrackingNumber] -.-> A1
    WA[Logistics_FleetManagement] -.-> A1
    JMA[Logistics_DeliveryRoute] -.-> A2
    FA[Logistics_TrackingNumber] -.-> A2
    SA[Logistics_DeliveryRoute] -.-> A3
    RAA[Logistics_StockLevel] -.-> A4
    PA[Logistics_Warehouse] -.-> A5
    
    %% Editorial Journey
    E1[Logistics_Warehouse] --> E2[Logistics_FleetManagement]
    E2 --> E3[Logistics_TrackingNumber]
    E3 --> E4[Logistics_Warehouse]
    E4 --> E5[Logistics_StockLevel]
    
    %% Autonomous Agents for Editors
    TA[Logistics_Warehouse] -.-> E1
    RMA[Logistics_StockLevel] -.-> E2
    MA[Logistics_FleetManagement] -.-> E3
    DSA[Logistics_FleetManagement] -.-> E4
    HA[Logistics_DeliveryRoute] -.-> E5
    
    %% Reviewer Journey
    R1[Logistics_FleetManagement] --> R2[Logistics_StockLevel]
    R2 --> R3[Logistics_StockLevel]
    
    %% Autonomous Agents for Reviewers
    IAA[Logistics_TrackingNumber] -.-> R1
    AA[Logistics_TrackingNumber] -.-> R2
    QA[Logistics_StockLevel] -.-> R2
    SUA[Logistics_Warehouse] -.-> R3
    
    %% Journal Manager Journey
    J1[Logistics_FleetManagement] --> J2[Logistics_DeliveryRoute]
    J2 --> J3[Logistics_TrackingNumber]
    
    %% Autonomous Agents for Managers
    ANA[Logistics_StockLevel] -.-> J1
    QMA[Logistics_StockLevel] -.-> J2
    POA[Logistics_Warehouse] -.-> J3
    
    %% Workflow Stages
    WS1[Logistics_TrackingNumber] --> WS2[Logistics_TrackingNumber]
    WS2 --> WS3[Logistics_DeliveryRoute]
    WS3 --> WS4[Logistics_FleetManagement]
    WS4 --> WS5[Logistics_DeliveryRoute]
    
    %% Connections between journeys and stages
    A3 --> WS1
    E1 --> WS1
    E2 --> WS2
    E2 --> WS3
    R1 --> WS3
    E4 --> WS4
    E5 --> WS5
    
    %% Agent Coordination
    AC[Logistics_StockLevel] -.-> RA
    AC -.-> TA
    AC -.-> RMA
    AC -.-> ANA

    classDef authorClass fill:#e1f5fe,stroke:#01579b,stroke-width:2px

    classDef reviewerClass fill:#e8f5e8,stroke:#1b5e20,stroke-width:2px
    classDef managerClass fill:#fff3e0,stroke:#e65100,stroke-width:2px
    classDef agentClass fill:#ffebee,stroke:#c62828,stroke-width:2px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    classDef stageClass fill:#f1f8e9,stroke:#33691e,stroke-width:3px
    classDef coordinatorClass fill:#fce4ec,stroke:#880e4f,stroke-width:3px
    
    class A1,A2,A3,A4,A5 authorClass
    class E1,E2,E3,E4,E5 editorClass
    class R1,R2,R3 reviewerClass
    class J1,J2,J3 managerClass
    class RA,WA,JMA,FA,SA,RAA,PA,TA,RMA,MA,DSA,HA,IAA,AA,QA,SUA,ANA,QMA,POA agentClass
    class WS1,WS2,WS3,WS4,WS5 stageClass
    class AC coordinatorClass
